casebody.data:
Wallace C. JONES, Jr., petitioner,
v.
FLORIDA. No. 13-8636. Supreme Court of the United States April 21, 2014.

Case below, 129 So.3d 1078.

Motion of petitioner for leave to proceed in forma pauperis denied, and petition for writ of certiorari to the District Court of *1884Florida, Third District, dismissed. See Rule 39.8.
